fields.title: Welcome Message
fields.message:
Welcome to iChat, A chat app that helps you connect with friends and family.

There are many enjoyable features contained within this app like;

  • Private Chat Message (with media features)
  • Group Chat Message (with media features)
  • Chat with AI (ChatGPT)
  • Status Updates
  • And many more...

We hope you enjoy the app and please do not forget to give us your feedback to help us provide better services to you.

Best Regards, Rigan.
